0.8.1:
- initial public release 

0.8.2:
- fixed minor bug in NBC_Iallgatherv()
- added full Fortran bindings (use cmake)
- improved performance of NBC_{Test,Wait}
- MPI_IN_PLACE support

0.9.1:
- new buildsystem (autoconf)
- enhanced Fortran bindings

0.9.2:
- OFED low-level interface
- better large-message allreduce algorithm (shift pattern)

0.9.3:
- full profiling layer support

0.9.4:
- threading works for MPI_THREAD_MULTIPLE implementations

0.9.5:
- OFED threaded support
- real-time thread option
